# Productionize qmd as the Knowledge Projection

## Question

Spike adopted (evaluate-qmd-brain-recall). Make it real: collections managed
from `brain-roots.json` (registration = indexing, one source of truth),
update hooks aligned to dark-wizard pulls + observer publishes, svx
frontmatter/component chunk-pollution mitigation, privacy boundary (sensitive
pages recallable locally only — define the caller contract before any MCP
exposure beyond flagg), MCP wiring for Claude/pi agents, a `joelclaw recall`
lane or alias, and re-embed cadence (36s full — can run per-publish).
Brainbench: add a qmd leg so knowledge-recall quality is measured, not
vibes.
